parameters: This place sometimes has a good view. Hehehe...

This house had a ghostly disturbance, yet a female weaver is still
living here calmly. It's strange...
Huh? Where did they go? Sorry, I don't know.

It's a big city, as you would expect from a former capital. There are
many winding roads, and when I first came here, I got lost many times.
But that's also the charm of a historic city.

……Even though it has such an old-fashioned atmosphere, it would be
ruined if a promiscuous girl was wandering around.
By the way, how can you stand the cold?

By the way, your outfit is quite flashy...or rather...is there some
kind of store like that around here? Well, that could be enjoyable in
its own way.
By the way, how come you're not cold?

Red-haired girl... Hmm, I do remember seeing her, but... I'm just a
stranger here, I don't think I can be of any help.
Hey, you... That's a bit... Put some clothes on...

Wait, are you telling me that even though you're a nun, you're
doing some strange job...?
……Enicia: Are you waiting for someone to comment on your outfit?
Hey, hey... Could you wear something a bit more...?

You were pretending to be passed out and got groped by a
pervert the other day, right? Aren't you a bit too careless?

It's okay. I swear in the name of God that I will never experience
such a thing again.

Are the children from the orphanage missing? \n[12] ...I haven't seen
anything, but I hope they're safe.

Damn it... I got my wallet stolen by some kid on a shady street...
Thanks to that, my tab at the bar has increased again...

Hm? Oh, you're that polite kid, Enicia. Come to think of it, I feel
like I passed by here before. You should have gone towards the market.

Do you know the child who lives in the house to the northwest? That
child always buys suspicious things at the market, like blackened
salamanders and poisonous plants.
I-I don't want to see that... it's embarrassing...
Why a swimsuit? Well, sure, you have a good figure but...

……Uwah... you're wearing something amazing... Is it really okay to wear
something like that?

……Uwah... you're wearing something amazing... Is it really okay to wear
something like that?

……Do kids from the church eat surprisingly good food? I mean, their skin
is beautiful and their figures are amazing... If I join the Church of
Seiros, maybe I can be like that too...

\n[12]-Chan? Ah, that's the red-haired girl like me. Hmm, I feel like
I've seen her before... but I don't know where she went.

I've traveled to many places, but there are strangely many monsters
around this town. It seems that they started increasing recently, and
it's unnatural. I hope nothing strange happens...

I've traveled to many places, but there are strangely many monsters
around this town. It seems that they started increasing recently, and
it's unnatural. I hope nothing strange happens...

Hm? Are you looking for someone? Unfortunately, I have been traveling
and I am not familiar with this place.

……Hmph, I'm not Enicia from the church. Are you still smiling at
everyone and making them mistake you for a man?
Heh, I-I'm not grinning... It's not like I meant to...

Walking around like that is not convincing at all. ...In fact, it's so
perverted that it's repulsive...

Walking around like that is not convincing at all. Just as I thought,
you're a lewd woman.

Walking around like that is not convincing at all. Just as I thought,
you're a lewd woman.

Walking around like that is not convincing at all. Just as I thought,
you're a lewd woman.

Well, whatever. There are plenty of men targeting you, Enicia. It's
good to be kind, but be careful, okay?

\n[12] That cute red-haired girl who always greets us, right? ...I
don't think she's around here. Why don't we try looking at the market?
That girl is kinda dangerous... She's always mumbling something...

That guy from \n[25], he's been doing unusually well lately... Even
though he doesn't seem to be working any harder than usual. It's
suspicious...

\n[12]-Chan...? Sorry, I haven't seen anything today. Did something
happen?
Hmmm...the Rista Church, huh? Maybe I should go pray there sometime.

The red-haired girl? I did see her, but... I just got off here, so I
don't know where she went...

I heard they lifted the lockdown on the lower part of the shady
street. Now we can finally go to the brothel without taking a
detour...

Seriously? I can't keep going like this. Is it Tito-chan tonight? Or
should I go with Setsuka-chan?
